  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ranged Tactics Toolbox pg. 18</em></p>\n<h3 class=\"framing\"><img style=\"margin: 3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\" src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" />Statistics</h3>\n<p><strong>Cost</strong> 250 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 6 lbs.</p>\n<p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d6 (small), 1d8 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> 19-20/x2; <strong>Range</strong> 80 ft.; <strong>Type</strong> P; <strong>Special</strong> -</p>\n<p><strong>Category</strong> Ranged; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p>\n<h3 class=\"framing\">Description</h3>\n<p>This weapon functions as a @Compendium[pf1.weapons-and-ammo.0MFbQaJ3MUWV2fGM]{Heavy Crank Crossbow}, except that its damage, critical, and range values are equivalent to those of a @Compendium[pf1.weapons-and-ammo.RWbjRwSPsuPAUDhw]{Light Crossbow}. Its lighter construction means it provides only a +1 bonus on @Compendium[pf1.skills.xvua9V5Zggkc77Gt]{Climb} checks and grapple combat maneuver checks to pull the target toward you.</p>",
